instance ChargesAddCommGroup (χ : ACCSystemCharges) : AddCommGroup χ.Charges :=
  Module.addCommMonoidToAddCommGroup ℚ

/-!

### B.2. The finiteness of the `ℚ`-module structure on `Charges`

The type `χ.Charges` is a finite module.

